    "The most NC/A-O task categories include brainstorming, explanation, logic and maths, as well as creativity and creative writing.",
    "In comparison, the most commercially viable task categories are short text generation, translation and classification.",
    "Similarly, among source domains, governments and search queries are largely viable for commercial (and unspecified) purposes, whereas general web, exams and model-generated sources are among the most restrictive.",
    "Not only do NC/A-O datasets appear more textually and functionally diverse, their length characteristics differ substantially.",
    "While Table 3 shows the input text lengths across licence categories are similar on average, the target text lengths are higher for NC/A-O datasets (103 versus 677)."
